column10: If you agree to voluntarily participate in this research project as described, please indicate your agreement by selecting “Yes, I volunteer” below.  Please print (or save a pdf of) this consent form for your reference. Thank you for your participation.
column11: With this research, we hope to see how individual student mental wellness changes over the course of an engineering program. We plan to use this data to try to improve the experience of future students. With this in mind, we may wish to invite you to participate in a one-on-one interview with one of the researchers, for which you will be compensated with a $40 amazon.com gift card! We would also like to contact you for follow-up surveys next Fall and the Fall after. If you're willing to be contacted, please provide us with a permanent email address and your school email address.
